Hello,

This email message is a notification to let you know that
a file has been uploaded to the Files area of the neat 
group.

  File        : /neatwin2.zip 
  Uploaded by : zysyshelp <zysyshelp@...> 
  Description : A version of NEAT which will compile under Windows with Cygwin and SWIG, using the normal make utility. Also included are Visual C++ files for editing source (although you can't use these to compile NEAT). As this is just a copy of my own NEAT folder, it has my experiments and gene files included. Also includes the weight capping feature and dynamic compat_thresh. This version fixes a problem I introduced into genetics.cpp. 

You can access this file at the URL

http://groups.yahoo.com/group/neat/files/neatwin2.zip
